sequenceDiagram
  participant User
  participant EditScreenInfo
  participant UI
  participant ExternalLink

  User->>EditScreenInfo: Open Screen
  EditScreenInfo->>UI: Display Path & Instructions

  User->>EditScreenInfo: Modify Code & Save
  EditScreenInfo->>UI: Automatically Update App

  User->>ExternalLink: Tap Help Link
  ExternalLink->>User: Redirect to Expo Docs
